<Body><Title>椹川大道北与康强路交汇处发生重大交通事故 致2死1伤</Title>
<ReportTime type="absTime">2013-04-17</ReportTime>

<Content>
<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">碧海银沙网</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d1">讯</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e2"><Time type="relTime" tid="t2">今天（17日）下午</Time>起，<Participant sid="s2">梁姓、李姓、苏姓、陈姓、吴姓等市民</Participant>纷纷<Denoter type="operation" did="d2">来电</Denoter></Event>，
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e3">说<Location lid="l3">赤坎椹川大道北</Location>发生重大<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e4">><Object sid="s4">“巡城马”</Object>迅速到场<Denoter type="operation" did="d4">采访</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
</Paragraph>
<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e5">一辆<Object sid="s5，s6，s7">“鱼峰”大型水泥搅拌车</Object>从霞山方向<Denoter type="movement" did="d5">行至</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l5">椹川大道北</Location></Event>
右转康强路时突然<Event eid="e6"><Denoter type="action" did="d6">侧翻</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e7"><Denoter type="action" did="d7">倒地</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e8">一骑自行车<Participant oid="o8">老人</Participant>和<Participant oid="o8">小女孩</Participant>被倾泻的<Object sid="s8">水泥和石子</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d8">埋</Denoter>了半截</Event>
并<Event eid="e9"><Location lid="l9">当场</Location><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">死亡</Denoter></Event>,
而<Event eid="e10">一骑电动车<Participant oid="o10">妇女</Participant>被<Object sid="s10">车头</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d10">撞</Denoter>上</Event>
并<Event eid="e11">被<Object sid="s11">车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d11">轧住</Denoter><Object oid="o11">右脚</Object></Event>，导致因<Event eid="e12"><Denoter type="action" did="d12">碎裂</Denoter></Event>
而<Event eid="e13">严重<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
</Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e14"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d14">事故</Denoter>发生在<Location lid="l14">椹川大道北与康强路交汇处</Location></Event>。
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e15">据不少<Participant sid="s15">目击者</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d15">介绍</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e16"><Time type="relTime" tid="t16">下午两点半左右</Time>，一辆<Object sid="s16">“鱼峰”大型水泥搅拌车</Object>从霞山方向行至<Location lid="l16">椹川大道北右转康强路</Location>时突然<Denoter type="operation" did="d16">侧翻倒地</Denoter></Event>，
致使<Event eid="e17">车上<Object sid="s17">水泥和石子</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d17">倾泻</Denoter>于<Location lid="l17">路面</Location></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e18">令人惨不忍睹的是：<Object sid="s18">整车</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d18">翻倒</Denoter>的瞬间</Event>，
<Event eid="e19">先是<Object sid="s19">车头</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d19">撞上</Denoter>迎面而来的一名40岁左右骑电动车的<Participant oid="o19">妇女</Participant></Event>，
并<Event eid="e20"><Denoter type="action" did="d20">轧住</Denoter><Object oid="o20">其右脚</Object></Event>，
导致<Event eid="e21"><Object sid="s21">其脚</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d21">碎裂</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e22">严重<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d22">受伤</Denoter></Event>；
接着<Event eid="e23"><Object sid="s23">车身及倾泻的水泥</Object>将刚好从车身旁经过的骑自行车的一60岁左右<Participant oid="o23">老人</Participant>和约十二三岁的<Participant oid="o23">小女孩</Participant><Denoter type="action" did="d23">埋</Denoter>了半截</Event>，
导致<Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24">老人和小女孩</Participant><Location lid="l24">当场</Location><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d24">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e25"><Participant sid="s25，s26，s27">司机</Participant>则<Denoter type="action" did="d25">敲碎</Denoter><Object oid="o25">车窗</Object></Event>
<Event eid="e26">自行<Denoter type="operation" did="d26">逃出</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e27">只受<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d27">轻伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　<Paragraph>　<Sentence>事故发生后，<Event eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28，s29，s31，s33，s34，s35">市、赤坎区公安，交警、消防</Participant>等火速到场<Denoter type="operation" did="d28">处置</Denoter></Event>。
<Event eid="e29">骑电动车<Participant oid="o29，o30">妇女</Participant>被立即<Denoter type="movement" did="d29">送到</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l29">医院</Location></Event>
<Event eid="e30"><Denoter did="d30" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e31">又<Denoter type="operation" did="d31">调来</Denoter><Object oid="o31，s32">4辆大型吊车</Object></Event>
将<Event eid="e32"><Object oid="o32">水泥搅拌车</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d32">吊起</Denoter></Event>，
将<Event eid="e33">被轧的<Participant oid="o33">老人和小女孩</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d33">救</Denoter>出来</Event>
并<Event eid="e34"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d34">急救</Denoter></Event>，
<Event polarity="negative" eid="e35">但最终无法<Denoter type="operation" did="d35">救回</Denoter>两人的<Object oid="o35">生命</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 　<Paragraph>　<Sentence>现场人山人海。<Event eid="e36"><Time type="relTime" tid="t36">目前</Time>，具体的<Object oid="o36">事故原因</Object>正在全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d36">侦察</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence>
 </Paragraph>
